Create a complete e-commerce web application called "ShopFlow" with the following specifications:

### BRAND & DESIGN
- Name: ShopFlow
- Style: Modern glassmorphism with purple-blue gradients (#667eea to #764ba2)
- Font: Inter (Google Fonts)
- Background: Animated gradient blobs (purple, blue, pink) with blur effects
- Cards: White/transparent with backdrop-blur, rounded-2xl, shadow-lg
- Buttons: Rounded-full, gradient backgrounds, hover:scale-105 transitions

### PRODUCT CATALOG
Display 8 products in a responsive grid (1 col mobile, 2 cols tablet, 4 cols desktop):

1. Casque Audio  - 299€ - Tech - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505740420928-5e560c06d30e?w=400
2. Montre Connectée Pro - 449€ - Tech - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523275335684-37898b6baf30?w=400
3. Sac à Dos Urban - 89€ - Fashion - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553062407-98eeb64c6a62?w=400
4. Baskets Sport Air - 159€ - Fashion - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?w=400
5. Appareil Photo Instantané - 129€ - Tech - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526170375885-4d8ecf77b99f?w=400
6. Lampe Design Minimaliste - 79€ - Home - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507473885765-e6ed057f782c?w=400
7. Cafetière Italienne - 45€ - Home - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517080319804-137d2475d01f?w=400
8. Crème Hydratante Bio - 34€ - Beauty - https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556228720-195a672e8a03?w=400

Each product card shows: image, category badge, rating with star icon, name, price, and add-to-cart button.

### FILTERING & SEARCH
- Category filter buttons: All, Tech, Fashion, Home, Beauty (pill-shaped, active state highlighted)
- Real-time search bar in header (filters products instantly)

### SHOPPING CART
- Slide-out sidebar from right (fixed position, full height)
- List items with thumbnail, name, price, quantity controls (+/-), remove button
- Total price calculation at bottom
- "Checkout" button opens payment modal
- Cart icon in header with item count badge (animated bounce on add)

### PAYMENT SYSTEM (3 options)

**Option 1: Mobile Money (Primary)**
- Operator selection: MTN Mobile Money (yellow #FFCC00), Orange Money (orange #FF6600), Wave (blue #00B4DB)
- Phone number input with country code detection
- PIN validation simulation (4-6 digits)
- Processing animation (3 seconds)
- Success confirmation with checkmark animation

**Option 2: Credit Card**
- Card number input with formatting
- Expiry date and CVC fields
- Pay button with amount display

**Option 3: Cash on Delivery**
- Confirmation message
- Order summary

### INTERACTIONS & ANIMATIONS
- Product cards: lift up + shadow increase on hover
- Add to cart: button scale animation + toast notification "Product added!"
- Cart sidebar: smooth slide transition (300ms ease-out)
- Page load: staggered fade-in animation for products
- Background: slowly floating gradient orbs (continuous animation)

### TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS
- React with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Lucide React for icons (ShoppingCart, Star, Plus, Minus, X, Check, Smartphone, CreditCard)
- useState for cart management and UI state
- Framer Motion for smooth animations
- Fully responsive (mobile-first)

### COMPONENTS STRUCTURE
- Header: logo, search bar, cart icon with badge
- Hero: title with gradient text, subtitle
- FilterBar: category pills
- ProductGrid: responsive grid of ProductCards
- ProductCard: image, info, add button
- CartSidebar: overlay + slide panel
- CheckoutModal: payment method selection + forms
- Toast: notification system

### DELIVERABLE
Single-file React application (App.tsx) that can be exported and deployed to Netlify/Vercel immediately.
Moubarak 
